="0" valign="top">Preparation of document evidencing a lease search <LeaderRightJustified leader="dot" /></entry><entry align="right" colname="3" colsep="0" rowsep="0" valign="bottom">10.00</entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></TableGroup></Schedule></Regulation>